      • setCalendarNavigateButtonEvents

        private void setCalendarNavigateButtonEvents()
        Sets actions for calendar navigation buttons. Previous button goes back one month or week depending on toggle selected. Next does the same but for one month or week forward.

      • setAppointmentEditingButtonEvents

        private void setAppointmentEditingButtonEvents()
        Sets actions for appointment add, edit, and delete buttons. Add/edit trigger navigation to their pages and delete asks for user confirmation before doing so.

      • refreshCache

        private void refreshCache()
                   throws java.sql.SQLException
        Clears local cache then repopulates with data from database
        Throws:
        java.sql.SQLException - in case data could not be retrieved or database connection couldn't be established

      • setAppointmentTableListener

        private void setAppointmentTableListener()
        Sets listener for appointments table. Adds validation prefix to ensure edit/delete functions aren't executed with null selections and sets selected appointment to pass down to edit and delete pages.

      • setAppointmentColumns

        private void setAppointmentColumns()
        Sets columns in appointment table to relevant data from Appointment class
